     fhir:Narrative.div "<div xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\"><p class=\"res-header-id\"><b>Generated Narrative: CodeSystem oversight-reason</b></p><a name=\"oversight-reason\"> </a><a name=\"hcoversight-reason\"> </a><p>This case-sensitive code system <code>https://oversight-on-fhir.org/fhir/CodeSystem/oversight-reason</code> defines the following codes:</p><table class=\"codes\"><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\"><b>Code</b></td><td><b>Display</b></td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">clinical-disagreement<a name=\"oversight-reason-clinical-disagreement\"> </a></td><td>Clinician disagrees with the clinical judgment</td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">missing-information<a name=\"oversight-reason-missing-information\"> </a></td><td>The agent lacked information the clinician has</td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">patient-specific-factor<a name=\"oversight-reason-patient-specific-factor\"> </a></td><td>A patient-specific consideration the agent did not weigh</td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">data-vintage<a name=\"oversight-reason-data-vintage\"> </a></td><td>The clinician has newer data than the agent did</td></tr></table></div>"
